WEBVTT

00:02.567 --> 00:05.570
There are over 6 billion
people on planet Earth.

00:06.292 --> 00:08.727
Ordinary folks
like you and me,

00:09.058 --> 00:10.759
but if you look around
carefully,

00:11.087 --> 00:13.673
you might find that some
of these ordinary folks

00:13.707 --> 00:15.677
have extraordinary abilities.

00:16.703 --> 00:19.639
I call them Alphas.

00:19.671 --> 00:21.972
Some Alphas,
like the ones I work with,

00:22.006 --> 00:24.338
can do things
that would amaze you.

00:26.740 --> 00:30.573
Others--the angry,
the lost, the afraid--

00:30.608 --> 00:34.582
have abilities that frankly
can be terrifying.

